@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080
@permissionId = 1
@roleId = 1
@menuId = 1

### 권한 생성
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/permissions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "roleId": {{roleId}},
  "menuId": {{menuId}},
  "canRead": true,
  "canCreate": true,
  "canUpdate": false,
  "canDelete": false,
  "enabled": true
}

### 권한 목록 조회
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/permissions
Accept: application/json

### 권한 단건 조회
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/permissions/{{permissionId}}
Accept: application/json

### 권한 수정
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/permissions/{{permissionId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "roleId": {{roleId}},
  "menuId": {{menuId}},
  "canRead": true,
  "canCreate": true,
  "canUpdate": true,
  "canDelete": false,
  "enabled": true
}

### 권한 삭제
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/permissions/{{permissionId}}
Accept: application/json

### 삭제 후 권한 목록 조회
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/permissions
Accept: application/json

### 삭제 후 권한 단건 조회 예외 확인
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/permissions/{{permissionId}}
Accept: application/json
